<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">

<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Five Survive – Story Map</title>
<link href="./five-survive-story-map_files/css2" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --red: #c0392b;
    --dark-red: #7b1a12;
    --blood: #8b0000;
    --off-white: #e8e0d0;
    --dim: #a89880;
    --bg: #0a0806;
    --card: #110d0a;
    --border: #2a1a14;
  }

  body {
    background-color: var(--bg);
    font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
    color: var(--off-white);
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 40px 20px 60px;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Grain overlay */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.85' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='0.06'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 100;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  /* Blood drip lines */
  body::after {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 10%, var(--blood) 20%, var(--blood) 21%, transparent 22%, transparent 40%, var(--blood) 45%, var(--blood) 47%, transparent 48%, transparent 65%, var(--blood) 72%, var(--blood) 73%, transparent 74%);
    z-index: 99;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease forwards;
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* Header */
  .header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .header::after {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 120px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--red);
    margin: 18px auto 0;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--dim);
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease 0.2s both;
  }

  .title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 12vw, 8rem);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    line-height: 0.9;
    color: var(--off-white);
    text-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(192,57,43,0.3), 4px 4px 0 var(--dark-red);
    animation: fadeIn 1s ease 0.1s both;
  }

  .title span {
    color: var(--red);
  }

  .author {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--dim);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-top: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  /* Story label */
  .story-label {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.5em;
    color: var(--red);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  /* Grid */
  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    grid-template-rows: auto auto;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  /* Card */
  .card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 28px 30px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    animation: fadeIn 1s ease both;
  }

  .card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.45s; }
  .card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
  .card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.75s; }

  /* Red corner accent */
  .card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 4px;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--red), var(--dark-red));
  }

  /* Subtle bg number */
  .card::after {
    content: attr(data-num);
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -10px; right: 10px;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 7rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    line-height: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .card-tag {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.45em;
    color: var(--red);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    display: block;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--off-white);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .card-divider {
    width: 40px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .card-body {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #c8bfb0;
  }

  .card-body strong {
    color: var(--off-white);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Theories list */
  .theories-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .theories-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #c8bfb0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .theories-list li::before {
    content: '▸';
    color: var(--red);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    margin-top: 3px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* Hook card spans full width */
  .card.hook {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
  }

  .hook .card-body {
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  /* Atmosphere tag row */
  .atmo-tags {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 14px;
  }

  .atmo-tag {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 4px 12px;
    color: var(--dim);
  }

  /* Footer */
  .footer {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 44px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--dim);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    opacity: 0.6;
    animation: fadeIn 1s ease 1s both;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .card.hook { grid-column: 1; }
    .title { font-size: 4.5rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

  <header class="header">
    <p class="subtitle">Story Map</p>
    <h1 class="title">FIVE <span>SURVIVE</span></h1>
    <p class="author">by Holly Jackson</p>
  </header>

  <p class="story-label">— Eight Hours · Six Friends · Five Survive —</p>

  <div class="grid">

    <!-- Setting -->
    <div class="card" data-num="01">
      <span class="card-tag">01 · Where &amp; When</span>
      <h2 class="card-title">Setting</h2>
      <div class="card-divider"></div>
      <p class="card-body">
        The story takes place from <strong>April 9th to April 10th, 2022</strong>. It unfolds inside an <strong>RV</strong> stranded on a remote road in the <strong>USA</strong>, as the group drives from Philadelphia to Gulf Shores for spring break.
      </p>
      <div class="atmo-tags">
        <span class="atmo-tag">Mysterious</span>
        <span class="atmo-tag">Dark</span>
        <span class="atmo-tag">Unpredictable</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Protagonist -->
    <div class="card" data-num="02">
      <span class="card-tag">02 · Main Character</span>
      <h2 class="card-title">Protagonist</h2>
      <div class="card-divider"></div>
      <p class="card-body">
        The main character is <strong>Red Kenny</strong>. She is on a road trip with five friends: her best friend <strong>Maddy</strong>, Maddy's brother <strong>Oliver</strong>, Oliver's girlfriend <strong>Reyna</strong>, <strong>Simon</strong>, and <strong>Arthur</strong>. At the beginning it seems like a typical teen vacation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Hook -->
    <div class="card hook" data-num="03">
      <span class="card-tag">03 · Main Conflict</span>
      <h2 class="card-title">Hook</h2>
      <div class="card-divider"></div>
      <p class="card-body">
        The main conflict starts when the RV <strong>suddenly breaks down in the middle of nowhere</strong>. Soon the group realizes they are being watched by a <strong>sniper</strong> who wants one of them to tell him a secret. The tension makes you keep reading — you want to know what happens next, <strong>who the sniper is</strong>, and who among them is hiding a secret.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Theories -->
    <div class="card" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;" data-num="04">
      <span class="card-tag">04 · Predictions</span>
      <h2 class="card-title">Theories</h2>
      <div class="card-divider"></div>
      <ul class="theories-list">
        <li>Someone will die before the night is over.</li>
        <li>Arthur and Red will become a couple.</li>
        <li>The friends will turn against each other.</li>
        <li>They will find a way out — call the police or escape.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>

  <p class="footer">"Not all of them will survive the night…"</p>

</div>


</body></html>
